item.title: Glass French Press in Gray
item.dc:creator: nguyenluan
item.description:
Product Specs: H5.4 x W 11.5 x D 6.3 / 40.5 oz Pan and Lid: Enamel Handle: Wood By Yield Design, a Florida-based design brand that lives at “the intersection of functionality and elegance, of high-end design and accessibility.” Their Glass French Press is an extraordinary piece. Note the premium borosilicate glass—there’s no plastic insight—which is heat-proof and resistant to thermal shock. Durable, yet delicate. Like all their products, it is ethically-produced.
  • High gloss finish on all interiors
  • Certified SGS Food Safe
